&lt;p&gt;The Continuing Care team in Camden is recruiting at an exciting time in Continuing Health Care. There is more understanding of continuing health care now more than ever before and a great opportunity to advocate for our clients and to ensure they are provided with the best care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The senior nurse assessor role is one of leadership – leading in a clinical area of continuing care and helping the team meet its objectives. You could be part of this vibrant team providing care and assessments for the multi-cultural and diverse population of Camden. We look forward to hearing from you.&lt;/p&gt;
